---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Services
seo:
  title: Vandore Heritage Services
  description: Explore the representation, relocation, and restoration services we deliver for owners and executive teams.
_enabled_editors:
  - visual
  - data
hero:
  eyebrow: Services
  headline: From mandate to move-in with one accountable team
  subheadline: Tailored programs for sellers, relocating teams, and restoration partners across Latvia.
  cta_label: Plan a strategy session
  cta_url: /contact/
services:
  - name: Heritage sales strategy
    summary: Positioning, marketing, and negotiation for significant properties with discretion.
    deliverables:
      - Comparative market storytelling
      - Multi-channel launch with privacy controls
      - Curated private viewings and briefing packs
  - name: Executive relocation
    summary: Short & long-term placements, cultural onboarding, and family support delivered as one program.
    deliverables:
      - Temporary residences with hospitality standards
      - School and community integration for families
      - Dedicated concierge and lifestyle support
  - name: Restoration partner program
    summary: Architect, artisan, and supplier alignment for heritage projects.
    deliverables:
      - Conservation blueprint and risk mapping
      - Craft tendering and oversight
      - Sustainability and technology integration review
cta:
  heading: Ready to align on your next brief?
  description: Share the contours of your mandate and our team will prepare a confidential proposal within two business days.
  label: Start your brief
  url: /contact/
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.eyebrow">{{ hero.eyebrow }}</p>
    <h1 data-cms-bind="#hero.headline">{{ hero.headline }}</h1>
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.subheadline">{{ hero.subheadline }}</p>
    <a class="cta" href="{{ hero.cta_url }}"><span data-cms-bind="#hero.cta_label">{{ hero.cta_label }}</span></a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container grid two">
    {% for service in services %}
    <article class="card" data-cms-collection="services" data-cms-item="{{ loop.index0 }}">
      <h2 data-cms-bind="name">{{ service.name }}</h2>
      <p data-cms-bind="summary">{{ service.summary }}</p>
      <ul>
        {% for deliverable in service.deliverables %}
        <li><span data-cms-bind="deliverables[{{ loop.index0 }}]">{{ deliverable }}</span></li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section alt">
  <div class="container card">
    <h2 data-cms-bind="#cta.heading">{{ cta.heading }}</h2>
    <p data-cms-bind="#cta.description">{{ cta.description }}</p>
    <a class="cta" href="{{ cta.url }}"><span data-cms-bind="#cta.label">{{ cta.label }}</span></a>
  </div>
</section>


